  "text": "We introduce the novel Attention Guided Graph Convolutional Networks (AGGCNs). Experimental results show that AGGCNs achieve state-ofthe-art results on various relation extraction tasks. Unlike previous approaches, AGGCNs operate directly on the full tree and learn to distill the useful information from it in an end-to-end fashion. There are multiple venues for future work. One natural question we would like to ask is how to make use of the proposed framework to perform improved graph representation learning for graph related tasks [CITATION_1] .",
